  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Bring Safe Water to School Kids in Vietnam</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Many children in Vietnam lack access to water that is safe for both drinking and handwashing. Water that looks clean may still have bacteria that is invisible to the human eye that makes it unsafe for drinking, and causes illness and disease. Hygiene education in schools is also lacking and diseases such as diarrhea are common. MEDRIX creates a healthy future for Vietnamese kids by installing water filtration systems for drinking water and handwashing stations in preschools and primary schools.</narrative>
  </description>
